/>\n下次要寫齊中英對照再加全學名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會，G6PD好撚出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇開既都識<br />\n如果個醫生連G6PD都唔識，我建議你即刻走算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15dadc25af922670b78fe52c6849e74359d462de","tid":361204,"uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果我寫g6pd會唔會又比錯藥架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個會死人架喎<br />\n<br />\n下次要寫齊中英對照再加全學名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港醫護用開 g6pd 呢個term<br />\n反而乜尻氯霉素氰霉素呢d支那字眼，香港醫護唔會用"},{"pid":"2cf834cf9897698329febf754bec63976ab693ce","tid":361204,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:19:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e234f54354b2b7e9679730f2b23d1fa4e45547a3","tid":361204,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:21:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會個新移民 &quot;青&quot; 同 &quot;綠&quot; 當咗一樣...<br />\n點知又真係有另一隻叫 &quot;氯&quot;霉素...</blockquote><br />\n似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n九成係"},{"pid":"6d72d3b121986f5dc7a46489ce5a15a1c50dac16","tid":361204,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"藥物敏感卡<br />\n<br />\n係香港睇咁耐醫生都無人問過<br />\n通常佢問我，我就答藥名（有敏感果d）"},{"pid":"b73f2f2dc7a6167d008657bf1f9b6e3c899d78db","tid":361204,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:27:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><